## ğŸ“¦ Package Overview

### @plcl-core
Core component library with 45+ components:
- **Inputs**: Button, Input, Textarea, Select, Checkbox, Switch, Radio, Slider
- **Display**: Card, Badge, Avatar, Alert, Progress, Loading, Skeleton
- **Layout**: Container, Box, Grid, Flex, Stack, Group, Divider, Spacer
- **Navigation**: Menu, Burger, NavigationMenu, SidebarNavigation
- **Overlay**: Modal, Drawer, Popover, Tooltip
- **Data**: Accordion
- **Interface**: Header, Footer, Sidebar, Main, AppIcon
- **Typography**: Text, Title, Code, Blockquote, Kbd
- **Theme**: ThemeProvider, useTheme

### @plcl-ui
Desktop UI layer:
- **Shell** - Main component with 6 variants:
  - `desktop` - Full OS-like environment
  - `app` - Standard app layout
  - `page` - Simple page layout
  - `sidebar` - Sidebar navigation
  - `web` - Iframe wrapper
  - `window` - Individual window
- **Internal Components**: Window, WindowManager, Settings, Search, Desktop, Wallpaper

---

## ğŸ“‹ Cross-Project Dependencies

- `@plcl/core-types` must be built before `@plcl/core`
- `@plcl/ui-types` must be built before `@plcl/ui`
- `@plcl/core` must be built before `@plcl/ui`
- `docs` and `playground` depend on all library packages

---

## ğŸ“ Notes

- All packages use npm workspaces for dependency management
- Build order: core-types â†’ core â†’ ui-types â†’ ui â†’ apps
- Shell component consolidates all desktop functionality
- Custom apps easily added via `customApps` prop

